                <p class="hero-subtitle">Here's what's happening at Aurelia Dental Clinic - Dr Jade today</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-shield-icon">
                <svg width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
